into an ecosystem, it is always altered.

00:29.680 --> 00:32.720
<i>The new one can devastate</i>
<i>the flora and fauna of a place,</i>

00:33.520 --> 00:35.280
<i>breed endlessly,</i>

00:35.720 --> 00:39.560
<i>or cause more subtle changes</i>
<i>which end up perverting everything.</i>

00:40.600 --> 00:44.120
